{"tid":1030361,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"Shamsung果對Galaxy Buds竟然有usb-c無TWS-plus，失望","createTime":"2019-02-21T01:29:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-21T03:29:20.000Z","uid":54481,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b15ecd91ec9e224b4cd4628ea7b73248464ca580","tid":1030361,"uid":54481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T01:29:22.000Z","msg":"難得有對真無線個盒係用usb-c，甚至可以無線充電<br />\n<br />\n屌拿星，三星又繼續係核心既位用返2手科技<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用舊chips，無TWS-plus，耗電又大，仲要唔support apt-x<br />\n對galaxy buds每邊5.6g，用得6個鐘，加埋個盒都只係多7個鐘<br />\n<br />\nAVIOT TE-D01有TWS-plus，重量只係每邊4.5g，可以用9個鐘，加埋盒有total81個鐘<br />\nMAVIN Air-X仲勁，一樣每邊4.5g，可以用10個鐘，加埋盒有total50個鐘<br />\n可惜AVIOT TE-D01同MAVIN Air-X都無usb-c<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93dc37bcc3c5072a79a490b288604cb5da44c62a","tid":1030361,"uid":15199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T02:43:21.000Z","msg":"e12<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5bb1e6f02989614e2c69aea2698b88edc895880","tid":1030361,"uid":54481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93dc37bcc3c5072a79a490b288604cb5da44c62a","tid":1030361,"uid":15199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T02:43:21.000Z","msg":"e12<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T02:49:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf516541da1f5b8a7f34c3de64df2a9ffe78fc53","tid":1030361,"uid":228532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T03:29:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}